budgies not talking i have had my budgie for a while now and i taught him how to say heaps of stuff he used to talk and chirp all day every day and now over the past few days he hasnt been talking or chirping at all he is also constantly puffed up hes poo is normal and hes eating not stop and drinking fine please help thanks in advance usually if a bird stops talking chirping its a good indication all is not well it could just be your bird is about to moult sometimes they puff up because they feel off colour moulting is a stressful time for a bird that said any change in your birds normal behaviour needs assessing by a vet its important to take your bird as soon as possible delay could affect your birds health Moult Budgerigar Chirp Chicken Capercaillie Species Non-Hodgkin's lymphoma Prostate cancer Tooth enamel Traffic light Childbirth Stuttering Past teachings of Prem Rawat Sesame Street Stomach cancer New Zealand English Bird ringing Shit Traumatic incident reduction Conker's Bad Fur Day Milton H. Erickson Radar Birdwatching Hearing impairment Sonar Fasting Anorexia nervosa Crayfish Second language acquisition Tai shogi Ancient Macedonian language Autism Neuro-linguistic programming The Amazing Race Tofu The SpongeBob SquarePants Movie Emu Unemployment The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy Primary and Secondary Phases Diarrhea Vitamin C Time Tai Chi Chuan Insect Mental illness Little Britain Chocolate Wetland Stoat Singlish Guinea pig Egg (food) Synthetic aperture radar Red Squirrel Condor Binge eating disorder Dispersion (optics) Eating disorder Jet engine Animal communication Seabird Indiana State University Insulin Norwegian Wood (This Bird Has Flown) Insomnia Psychology Places in The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy Mallard Bird Borderline personality disorder Color Feces Psychotherapy Garfield Famine Alcoholism Equine conformation Spanish verbs Wine Fecal incontinence 613 mitzvot Obsessive-compulsive disorder Canary Non-native pronunciations of English Mid-le